  "description": "This is a world where humans and monsters coexist. Legend has it that there are four treasures in the world that can grant any wish...but no one has ever found them, and most believe that they exist only in legend. One day, two young friends felt a strange power coming from a cave near their village. The power attracts monsters to the area, and they end up trapped in the cave...<br><br><i>Maze Heroes</i> is a hybrid RPG/board game. Players roll a number and move around on the paths, picking up items and encountering monsters and other players in turn-based battles. Players can choose to fight, cast magic, use items, or escape. The game features a single-player story mode as well as a multiplayer battle mode for up to four players.",
